<h2 style="color: #c9a84c; margin-top: 0;">Verify Your Email Address</h2>

<p>Hi {{name}},</p>

<p>
  Thank you for registering with the CSE SUST portal. To complete your registration
  and activate your account, please verify your email address by clicking the button below.
</p>

<div style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="btn">Verify Email Address</a>
</div>

<p>
  If the button above does not work, copy and paste the following link into your browser:
</p>

<div class="highlight">
  <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" style="word-break: break-all;">{{verificationUrl}}</a>
</div>

<p>
  This verification link will expire in <strong>24 hours</strong>. If you did not create
  an account on CSE SUST, please ignore this email.
</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br />
  <strong style="color: #c9a84c;">CSE SUST Team</strong>
</p>
